<div id=3D"outline-container-org2af621b" class=3D"outline-3">
<h3 id=3D"org2af621b">Alessandro Strada announced</h3>
<div class=3D"outline-text-3" id=3D"text-org2af621b">
<p>
Hi everyone,
</p>

<p>
I=E2=80=99m happy to announce that <code>google-drive-ocamlfuse</code> 0.9.=
0 is now available on opam.
</p>

<p>
This release migrates from <code>libfuse</code> 2 to <code>libfuse</code> 3=
, allowing the package to be installed on modern Linux distributions that n=
o longer provide <code>libfuse</code> 2.
</p>

<pre class=3D"example" id=3D"org8d22827">
opam update
opam install google-drive-ocamlfuse
</pre>

<p>
Repositories:
</p>

<ul class=3D"org-ul">
<li><a href=3D"https://github.com/astrada/google-drive-ocamlfuse"><code>goo=
gle-drive-ocamlfuse</code></a></li>
<li><a href=3D"https://github.com/astrada/ocamlfuse"><code>ocamlfuse</code>=
</a> =E2=80=94 OCaml bindings for <code>libfuse</code></li>
</ul>

<p>
Best,
Alessandro
</p>
