<div class=3D"outline-text-3" id=3D"text-orga201c41">
<p>
We have the pleasure of celebrating the birthday of Blaise Pascal by announ=
cing the release of OCaml version 5.5.0.
</p>

<p>
Some of the highlights in OCaml 5.5.0 are:
</p>
</div>
<div id=3D"outline-container-orgb96a426" class=3D"outline-4">
