: bold;">t</span> =3D <span style=3D"color: #242521;">Converge</span> | <sp=
an style=3D"color: #242521;">Escape</span> <span style=3D"color: #006f00; f=
ont-weight: bold;">of</span> int <span style=3D"color: #242521; font-weight=
: bold;">in</span>
  ...
  <span style=3D"color: #006f00; font-weight: bold;">match</span> orbit n x=
